  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this randomized trial is to investigate the effects of a 12-week yoga intervention
      compared to no specific intervention on weight-related outcomes, well-being, and health
      behaviour in 60 females with abdominal obesity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
